迈克尔·杰克逊传记片推迟至 2025 年底上映https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-jackson-biopic-delayed-to-late-2025-3809939?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=michael-jackson-biopic-delayed-to-late-2025Surej Singh Wed, 06 Nov 2024 04:10:16 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3809939 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>原定于明年四月首播</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-jackson-biopic-delayed-to-late-2025-3809939">迈克尔·杰克逊传记片推迟到 2025 年末</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首发。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/michael-jackson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>即将上映的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-jackson">迈克尔·杰克逊</a>传记片已推迟至 2025 年——了解更多信息如下。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="650" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/quincy-jones-obituary-3809386"><b>昆西·琼斯，1933-2024：眼中闪烁着光芒打破界限的超级制片人</b></a></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-jackson-biopic-in-the-works-by-bohemian-rhapsody-producer-3156367"><em>《迈克尔》</em></a>是 Antoine Fuqua 为狮门影业制作的下一个项目，原定于 2025 年 4 月在美国上映。现在， <a href="https://deadline.com/2024/11/michael-jackson-biopic-good-fortune-release-date-1236167786/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Deadline</em></a>证实狮门影业已经推迟了这部备受期待的传记片的上映，以便将这部电影定位在“颁奖走廊”。</p><p>该片目前定于 10 月 3 日在美国上映，全球首映日期尚未公布。 <em>《迈克尔》</em>将由环球影业在全球发行。</p><p>截至目前，有关这部电影的公开信息有限。它的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/michael-jackson-biopic-trailer-goes-down-well-with-critics-at-cinemacon-3616660">第一部预告片于四月份在 CinemaCon 上向评论家透露，据报道受到好评</a>，但尚未向公众发布。 </p><figure id="attachment_3785983" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3785983" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3785983" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Michael-Jackson-performing.jpg" alt="1996 年 7 月 16 日，迈克尔·杰克逊在文莱向估计 60,000 名观众表演。（照片来源应为 FRANCIS Sylvain/AFP via Getty Images）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Michael-Jackson-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Michael-Jackson-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Michael-Jackson-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Michael-Jackson-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Michael-Jackson-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Michael-Jackson-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3785983" class="wp-caption-text"> 1996 年 7 月 16 日，迈克尔·杰克逊在文莱向估计 60,000 名观众表演。（照片来源应为 FRANCIS Sylvain/AFP via Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>制片人格雷厄姆·金今年四月证实，该项目正处于制作中途。 “我们对这部电影感到无比自豪。我期待着为观众呈现一部他们从未见过的电影，”金说。</p><p>他还分享道：“当你提到他的名字时，每个人都有自己的看法。这是第一次……一代又一代的电影观众将齐聚一堂，深入了解这位有史以来最多产的艺术家。”</p><p>这部电影将讲述迈克尔·杰克逊的生活和职业生涯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-jackson-to-be-played-by-his-nephew-jaafar-in-upcoming-biopic-3389628">，由迈克尔·杰克逊的侄子贾法尔·杰克逊</a>主演。电影中的其他演员包括饰演乔·杰克逊的科尔曼·多明戈和饰演经理约翰·布兰卡的迈尔斯·特勒。</p><p> <em>《吸血鬼日记》</em>明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-vampire-diaries-star-to-portray-diana-ross-in-michael-jackson-biopic-3609373">凯特·格雷厄姆将饰演标志性的戴安娜·罗斯</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-producer-and-songwriter-quincy-jones-has-died-aged-91-3809203">本周早些时候去世的</a>行业巨头<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/quincy-jones">昆西·琼斯</a>将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/insecure"><em>《不安全</em></a>》的肯德里克·桑普森饰演。</p><p>到目前为止，电影中只发布了一张图片，贾法尔·杰克逊穿着迈克尔最具标志性的造型。您可以看到下图。 </p><figure id="attachment_3599127" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3599127" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3599127" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jaafar_jackson_2024.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jaafar_jackson_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jaafar_jackson_2024-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jaafar_jackson_2024-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jaafar_jackson_2024-696x1044.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jaafar_jackson_2024-1392x2088.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jaafar_jackson_2024-1068x1602.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3599127" class="wp-caption-text">贾法尔·杰克逊在《迈克尔》中饰演迈克尔·杰克逊。照片来源：凯文·马祖尔</figcaption></figure><p>就在电影推迟上映的消息传出后几天，迈克尔·杰克逊标志性专辑“Thriller”的联合制作人昆西·琼斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-producer-and-songwriter-quincy-jones-has-died-aged-91-3809203">去世，享年 91 岁</a>。</p><p>琼斯去世后，包括保罗·麦卡特尼、 <a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/stevie-wonder-quincy-jones-tribute-2-1235153268/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">史蒂夫·旺德</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/celine-dion-honours-musical-genius-and-cherished-mentor-quincy-jones-after-his-death-3809928">席琳·迪翁</a>在内的众多音乐巨星纷纷<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/quincy-jones-obituary-3809386">向这位传奇制作人致敬</a>。</p><p>在其他音乐电影新闻中，最近有消息称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknds-upcoming-film-with-jenna-ortega-and-barry-keoghan-to-tie-into-hurry-up-tomorrow-album-3809535">The Weeknd 即将与珍娜·奥尔特加 (Jenna Ortega) 和巴里·基奥根 (Barry Keoghan) 合作的电影将与这位加拿大音乐家即将发行的唱片《明天快点》(Hurry Up Tomorrow) 结合在一起</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-jackson-biopic-delayed-to-late-2025-3809939">迈克尔·杰克逊传记片推迟到 2025 年末</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首发。</p> ;
席琳·迪翁在昆西·琼斯去世后向“音乐天才”和“珍贵的导师”致敬https://www.nme.com/news/music/celine-dion-honours-musical-genius-and-cherished-mentor-quincy-jones-after-his-death-3809928?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=celine-迪翁在去世后荣获音乐天才和珍贵导师昆西·琼斯的荣誉Surej SinghWed, 06 Nov 2024 03:17:07 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3809928 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “他的影响力确实延伸到了全球各个角落”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/celine-dion-honours-musical-genius-and-cherished-mentor-quincy-jones-after-his-death-3809928">席琳·迪翁 (Celine Dion) 在去世后向“音乐天才”和“敬爱的导师”昆西·琼斯 (Quincy Jones) 致敬的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/celine-dion">席琳·迪</a>翁向她已故的“敬爱的导师”<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/quincy-jones">昆西·琼斯</a>致敬——看看她在下面怎么说。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="650" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/quincy-jones-obituary-3809386"><b>昆西·琼斯，1933-2024：眼中闪烁着光芒打破界限的超级制片人</b></a></li></ul><p>周一（11 月 4 日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-producer-and-songwriter-quincy-jones-has-died-aged-91-3809203">传奇制作人昆西·琼斯去世的消息传出，享年 91 岁</a>。随着他的去世，人们纷纷向这位已故偶像表示敬意。现在，席琳·迪翁也加入了这一行列，并在社交媒体上为琼斯写了一篇纪念文章。 </p><figure id="attachment_3809934" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3809934" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3809934" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones-2010@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones-2010@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones-2010@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones-2010@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones-2010@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones-2010@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones-2010@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3809934" class="wp-caption-text"> 2010 年，席琳·迪翁和昆西·琼斯一起在录音室。图片来源：Kevin Mazur/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>在 Instagram 上发布的一篇帖子中，附有两张她与已故制作人的照片以及两张她与琼斯合作的图片，她写道：“得知我的朋友、唯一的音乐天才昆西·琼斯去世的消息，我感到非常伤心。昆西既是一位我所珍视的导师，也是我尊敬的人，因为他对几乎所有形式的美国音乐都产生了深远的影响，这触动了我的世界。”</p><p> “我很荣幸能与昆西一起工作，这是梦想成真，”迪翁继续说道。 “在我们的会议中，他的音乐直觉非常深刻——他帮助我捕捉到了‘天堂的一小部分’。昆西总是确切地知道每首歌需要什么。</p><p> “除了他的善良和无数的成就之外，我还钦佩他的慈善工作，造福于艺术、全球饥荒和贫困青年。他的影响力确实延伸到了全球各个角落！”</p><p>请参阅下面席琳迪翁的完整帖子。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCAKQFzxRVC/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w