ing="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3809206" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_quincyjones_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="昆西·琼斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_quincyjones_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_quincyjones_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_quincyjones_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_quincyjones_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_quincyjones_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_quincyjones_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3809206" class="wp-caption-text">昆西·琼斯 图片来源：Greg Doherty/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>他还监督了 1985 年慈善唱片“We Are The World”的全明星录制，该唱片由杰克逊、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lionel-richie">莱昂内尔·里奇</a>和制作人迈克尔·奥马尔蒂安掌舵，并为 1985 年埃塞俄比亚的饥荒救济筹集了资金。</p><p>此后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>向琼斯致敬， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-mccartney-remembers-supremely-talented-quincy-jones-i-felt-privileged-to-have-known-him-3809499">并在社交媒体上写了一篇长篇致敬文章</a>，他回忆起通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>制作人乔治·马丁介绍给琼斯的经历，以及他“非常积极、充满爱心的精神”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-producer-and-songwriter-quincy-jones-has-died-aged-91-3809203">自从琼斯去世的消息传出后，众多向他致敬</a>的人包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nile-rodgers">尼罗·罗杰斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-caine">迈克尔·凯恩</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/will-smith">威尔·史密斯</a>等。</p><p>现任美国副总统兼总统候选人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kamala-harris-pays-tribute-to-trailblazer-quincy-jones-3809600">卡马拉·哈里斯也向昆西·琼斯致敬，称他为“开拓者”，</a>并承认他对“公民权利和人权”的贡献。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/celine-dion-honours-musical-genius-and-cherished-mentor-quincy-jones-after-his-death-3809928">席琳·迪翁 (Celine Dion) 在去世后向“音乐天才”和“敬爱的导师”昆西·琼斯 (Quincy Jones) 致敬的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
