那支球队的体育运动，但我认为它们都是同一个公司硬币的两面。</p><p> “从情感上来说，一个有色人种女性等等——当然，让我们把它排除在外，勾选那个框，这样我们就可以继续前进。但是，就人们真正想要的东西而言，两党都没有提供——他们只是控制了权力，”他继续说道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3488914" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3488914" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3488914" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-strokes-all-points-east-1@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-strokes-all-points-east-1@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-strokes-all-points-east-1@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-strokes-all-points-east-1@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-strokes-all-points-east-1@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-strokes-all-points-east-1@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-strokes-all-points-east-1@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3488914" class="wp-caption-text"> The Strokes 乐队的朱利安·卡萨布兰卡斯 (Julian Casablancas) 在 2023 年 All Points East Festival 音乐节上表演。图片来源：Jim Dyson/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查普尔·罗恩(Chappell Roan)</a>今年早些时候也发表过类似言论，当时她表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-on-why-she-feels-no-pressure-to-officially-endorse-a-presidential-candidate-3796272">，由于双方都存在“问题”，她不会在选举中全力支持任何一位候选人</a>。然而，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-clears-up-elections-stance-im-voting-for-fucking-kamala-3797165">后来表示她将投票给哈里斯</a>，尽管这并不一定意味着她支持副总统。</p><p>许多知名演员、艺术家和音乐家在选举前公开支持两位候选人。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂丝</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-endorses-kamala-harris-at-houston-rally-im-here-as-a-mother-3806513">上个月</a>在民主党关于生殖权利的集会上发表讲话，比莉·艾利什<a href="http://xn--her%20song%20when%20the%20partys%20over%20for%20a%20democrats%20ad%20on%20reproductive%20care-pw43didiv/">批准了她的歌曲</a>《When the Party&#39;s Over》为民主党生殖保健广告， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/avengers-cast-reunite-to-endorse-kamala-harris-kamala-forever-3808508">漫威《<i>复仇者联盟》</i>的演员们</a>在 Instagram 视频中重聚，为哈里斯背书。</p><p>其他正式认可哈里斯的人包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-shares-endorsement-for-kamala-harris-3808708">麦当娜</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/st-vincent-endorses-kamala-harris-says-her-grandmother-wouldnt-have-stood-for-disrespect-from-trump-3808930">圣文森特</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jennifer-lopez-on-puerto-rican-heritage-after-trump-rally-joke-we-are-americans-3809017">詹妮弗·洛佩兹</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-john-legend-and-more-endorse-kamala-harris-for-us-president-3776745">查理·XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joni-mitchell-shares-her-thoughts-on-the-us-elections-fuck-donald-trump-3804542">乔尼·米切尔</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-on-eve-of-us-election-3809580">Lady Gaga</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cher-endorses-kamala-harris-im-so-grateful-to-be-able-to-make-my-voice-count-this-year-3804267">雪儿</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-speaks-at-kamala-harris-rally-hits-out-at-donald-trumps-comments-about-detroit-3804404">利佐</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/obama-raps-lose-yourself-verse-at-kamala-harris-rally-after-being-introduced-by-eminem-3805325">阿姆</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/usher-joins-kamala-harris-at-atlanta-rally-everything-we-do-in-the-next-17-days-will-affect-our-children-and-grandchildren-3804493">亚瑟小子</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pnk-perform-what-about-us-with-daughter-to-close-democratic-national-convention-3786178">P!nk</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/leonardo-dicaprio">莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/leonardo-dicaprio-and-bad-bunny-have-endorsed-kamala-harris-3806836">坏兔子</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bon-iver-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-in-wisconsin-3781912">邦·伊弗</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/quavo-backs-kamala-harris-for-tackling-gun-violence-at-atlanta-rally-3779672">Quavo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-mumford-sons-push-for-voting-plan-as-they-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-3808418">Mumford &amp; Sons</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/these-are-glorillas-four-reasons-to-vote-for-kamala-harris-3807830">GloRilla</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Finneas">Finneas。</a></p><p>特朗普的知名支持者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kid-rock-shares-his-thoughts-on-taylor-swift-and-eminem-endorsing-kamala-harris-3807296">摇滚小子</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/kelsey-grammer-banned-from-talking-about-trump-support-in-interviews-reporter-claims-3553743">凯尔西·格拉默</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-makes-a-brief-appearance-at-donald-trump-supporters-rally-in-beverly-hills-3784869">坎耶·维斯特</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/hulk-hogan-asks-crowd-if-they-want-him-to-body-slam-kamala-harris-3786054">浩克·霍根</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-strokes-julian-casablancas-on-why-he-refused-to-vote-the-two-parties-are-a-joke-a-horrible-lie-3809913">The Strokes 的朱利安·卡萨布兰卡斯 (Julian Casablancas) 就拒绝投票的原因发表了一篇文章：“两个政党是一个笑话——一个可怕的谎言”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Joy Orbison 因放弃 Radiohead 歌曲《Creep》的 baile funk 混音而走红https://www.nme.com/news/music/joy-orbison-goes-viral-for-dropping-baile-funk-remix-of-radioheads-creep-3809866?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=joy-orbison-因无线电头蠕变而流行的放克混音版Anagricel DuranWed, 06 Nov 2024 00:31:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsDanceElectroRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3809866 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joy-Orbison-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-Credit-Dave-Benett-and-Samir-Hussein-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乔伊·奥比森 (Joy Orbison) 和 Radiohead 的汤姆·约克 (Thom Yorke)。图片来源：Dave Benett 和 Samir Hussein，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joy-Orbison-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-Credit-Dave-Benett-and-Samir-Hussein-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joy-Orbison-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-Credit-Dave-Benett-and-Samir-Hussein-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joy-Orbison-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-Credit-Dave-Benett-and-Samir-Hussein-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joy-Orbison-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-Credit-Dave-Benett-and-Samir-Hussein-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joy-Orbison-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-Credit-Dave-Benett-and-Samir-Hussein-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joy-Orbison-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-Credit-Dave-Benett-and-Samir-Hussein-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “乔伊·奥比森 (Joy Orbison) 的《Creep》混音版放克混音让我彻底崩溃”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joy-orbison-goes-viral-for-dropping-baile-funk-remix-of-radioheads-creep-3809866">Joy Orbison 因放弃 Radiohead 的《Creep》的 baile funk 混音版而走红的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joy-Orbison-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-Credit-Dave-Benett-and-Samir-Hussein-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乔伊·奥比森 (Joy Orbison) 和 Radiohead 的汤姆·约克 (Thom Yorke)。图片来源：Dave Benett 和 Samir Hussein，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joy-Orbison-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-Credit-Dave-Benett-and-Samir-Hussein-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joy-Orbison-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-Credit-Dave-Benett-and-Samir-Hussein-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joy-Orbison-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-Credit-Dave-Benett-and-Samir-Hussein-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joy-Orbison-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-Credit-Dave-Benett-and-Samir-Hussein-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joy-Orbison-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-Credit-Dave-Benett-and-Samir-Hussein-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Joy-Orbison-and-Radioheads-Thom-Yorke.-Credit-Dave-Benett-and-Samir-Hussein-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joy-orbison">Joy Orbison</a>最近在纽约的 DJ 现场表演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Radiohead">Radiohead</a>的《Creep》的 baile funk 混音版，因而走红。</p><p>上周末（11 月 2 日），这位伦敦制作人（真名 Peter O&#39;Grady）接管了 Brooklyn Steel，为歌迷带来了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thom-yorke">Thom Yorke</a>及其合作者 1992 年热门歌曲的令人惊喜的混音版。这首歌的演绎从一首黑暗、怪异的摇滚歌曲变成了一首充满时髦、嘻哈风格的歌曲，约克的歌声在强劲的节奏背后充当着令人难以忘怀的低语。</p><p>一位粉丝在他们的 X/Twitter 账户上分享了当时的视频片段，写道：“我对 Joy Orbison 放克 Creep 的混音版感到迷失。” “嘿，这是我的曲目，”制作人 DJ Lukinhas 回应道，他创作了 Orbison 改编的混音版，并通过 Soundcloud 分享了该曲目的链接。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Joy Orbison 的《Creep》贝莱放克混音版让我彻底崩溃了<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f62d.png" alt="??" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/geNDJy6LL7">pic.twitter.com/geNDJy6LL7</a></p><p> - burialposter (@burialposter) <a href="https://twitter.com/burialposter/status/1852965092599476353?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 11 月 3 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">嘿，这就是我的轨迹<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f62d.png" alt="??" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/G5krdDVEAQ">https://t.co/G5krdDVEAQ</a></p><p> — dj lukinhas ((calmo)) (@hcetdm) <a href="https://twitter.com/hcetdm/status/1852976988207681965?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 11 月 3 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="RADIOHEAD - CREEP [DJ LUKINHAS] 2023 由 DJ LUKINHAS (( CALMO ))" width="696" height="400" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?visual=true&#038;url=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F1556117320&#038;show_artwork=true&#038;maxheight=1000&#038;maxwidth=696"></iframe></p><p>混音版让这位伦敦制作人的粉丝们对这首歌的评价褒贬不一。一些人称赞了这首歌，一位用户在推特上写道：“乔伊·奥比森不会做错事”，而另一位用户则补充道：“这真是太好了。”</p><p>尽管这首歌曲受到了好评，但一些歌迷却没有留下深刻的印象。一位用户写道：“我不喜欢它，但我很欣赏这是乔伊·奥比森（Joy Orbison）要做的事情，”而另一位用户则分享道：“这听起来很糟糕，怎么会有人喜欢它。”</p><p> Orbison 将于周六（11 月 23 日）和周六（11 月 30 日）在伦敦 Earth 演出两晚，您可以<a href="https://joyorbison.x-l.co/bio?fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAAaakEkTYyPnS2wpvxhvtkAuqHvH0UiEbYula_t91vzceltM4AOC9kfcCWLM_aem_3dtjokJWFvyFMySEmxbFhQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">前往此处</a>购买门票。</p><p>在其他新闻中，约克最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thom-yorke-really-doesnt-give-a-fuck-if-you-want-radiohead-to-return-3804946">声称，如果歌迷想看到 Radiohead 回归，他“真的不在乎”</a> 。在最近的一次采访中，当被问及对 Radiohead 歌迷对乐队未来的猜测有何看法时，约克回答道：“我不知道，也不在乎。”</p><p> “没有冒犯任何人的意思，谢谢你的关心，”他继续说道。 “但我认为我们已经赢得了做对我们有意义的事情的权利，而不必解释自己或对任何其他人关于我们应该做什么的历史想法负责。”</p><p>乐队贝斯手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-interview-colin-greenwood-how-to-disappear-photo-book-band-future-tour-3803426">科林·格林伍德 (Colin Greenwood) 最近在其新写真集《How To Disappear》发行前接受了<i>NME</i>采访</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radioheads-colin-greenwood-announces-photo-book-of-life-with-the-band-how-to-disappear-3607539"><i>，</i></a>并对乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-have-been-back-together-rehearsing-it-was-really-fun-3791835">今年夏天的重聚排练</a>进行了一些深入了解。</p><p>在此之前，他的兄弟<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jonny-greenwood-interview-the-smile-cutouts-radiohead-return-3801554">乔尼 (Jonny) 向<i>NME</i>表示</a>，他发现排练“有趣且自然”，但接着补充说，2025 年“没有计划”进行任何与 Radiohead 相关的事情，因为成员们都专注于“个人”项目”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joy-orbison-goes-viral-for-dropping-baile-funk-remix-of-radioheads-creep-3809866">Joy Orbison 因放弃 Radiohead 的《Creep》的 baile funk 混音版而走红的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
